    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div type="letter">
                <div type="text">
                    <opener/>
                    <div type="transcription">
                        <p>Potatoes in my field have been seized by the disease in its most virulent form, giving out a nauseous smell, perceptible in an adjoining field;<ref target="#foot.f2"/> <hi rend="italic">C. Darwin, Farnborough, July</hi> 13.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                
            </div>
            
            
            
            
            
            <div type="footnotes">
                <note xml:id="foot.f1">The year is established by the date of publication of this letter in <hi rend="italic">Gardeners’ Chronicle</hi>.</note>
                <note xml:id="foot.f2">Potato blight, caused by the oomycete (water mould) <hi rend="italic">Phytophthora infestans</hi>, appeared in the British Isles in 1845, leading to the Irish potato famine of 1846 (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_6854.xml">Salaman 1985</ref>, p. 291).</note>
            </div>
            
        
            
